               <scopecontent id="aspace_5bc8ffc72ef4e840050e988249627709">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Presenting a copy of his Columbiad, with, on verso, Barlow's copy of the reply of the Institute (Joachim Le Breton, perpetual secretary), Paris, France, October 15, 1808.</p>
